{"tid":1975881,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港第一間戲院","createTime":"2020-04-17T00:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T15:13:20.000Z","uid":41846,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7cddeeb13d3a6208d5ffdf7c5d18a88040334b07","tid":1975881,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:16:57.000Z","msg":"時光旅行一百年！百幾年前嘅香港打咭拍拖勝地？<br />\n<br />\n依家疫情咁勁，想睇場戲都焗住只可以屈喺屋企睇Netflix，不過諗深一層，即使唔係疫情影響，香港人又有幾耐冇去過戲院呢？唔係講緊商場入面嗰啲，而係 #一座獨立嘅戲院 ，就好似下圖咁。如果喺下圖間戲院睇完戲，唔知又會唔會忍唔住喺門口打返張咭呢？<br />\n<br />\n依間戲院叫奄派亞，即係帝國嘅意思，係香港 #最早 嘅三間戲院之一，佢嘅裝修雖然已經靚過唔少英國同澳洲嘅同期戲院，但當時嘅香港人其實都唔太鍾意、覺得佢設計到成個貨倉咁，一啲都唔精美，不過亦因為咁，奄派亞無行到高尚戲院路線、而係作為 #大眾戲院 經營，成為無論本地市民、駐港士兵都鍾意去休閒消遣嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n可惜奄派亞只係經營咗十幾年，今日原址就變成恆生銀行大廈，咁樣一拍埋睇，要諗想喺奄派亞戲院定恆生銀行門口影相嘅話，就算舊時嘅香港人話佢一啲都唔靚都好，我諗我都係會揀奄派亞嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/114253393549679/posts/118203123154706/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F114253393549679%2Fposts%2F118203123154706%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10IR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=896db765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/114253393549679/posts/118203123154706/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LxO6DmN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxO6DmN.jpg&h=5a47c5c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"021a781b8711f266ab24cf352e5664e511687fc8","tid":1975881,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"以為太平戲院最舊添"},{"pid":"d45bcb368a3a752d1525571d6a33f0b7745b79e5","tid":1975881,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0f8f46143ac50b30292dddc64e8a33d4cc427ec","tid":1975881,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2103c033c5477653336a083e788618fc5c7fc52f","tid":1975881,"uid":140221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91cbe5c36663bfd1546dbd57e56b3580a6e73a9","tid":1975881,"uid":273021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}